    "name": "SpaceAPI Collector",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "description": {
      "content": "The SpaceAPI Collector is a central directory API that aggregates endpoints from hackerspaces, makerspaces, fablabs, and similar community spaces around the world that implement the SpaceAPI standard. It returns a list of all registered spaces with their status endpoint URLs, validity status, names, and last-seen timestamps.\n\nContact Support:\n Email: spaceapi-team@chaospott.de",
